OBJECTNAME
Security Footage
END

LOOTABLE
True
END

NAMES
security footage
security tape
footage
tape
END

USABLE WITH
Tape Player
END

LOOK_AT
It's a black microfilm cassette.
The label says it's security footage from two weeks ago.
END

USE
You can't use the cassette on its own.
You'll need a working tape player if you want to watch the footage. 
END

USE***TAPEPLAYER
You insert the cassette into the tape player,
which accepts it with a series of business-like clicks.
END

COMBINE***TAPEPLAYER
You insert the cassette into the tape player,
which accepts it with a series of business-like clicks.
END
